              "attributes" : {
                "dxpStyle" : { },
                "markupText" : "<h2 class='govuk-heading-l'>Your exemptions register</h2><p class='govuk-body'>Your account holds all the exemptions that you have registered.<br><br>You should make sure you read the guidance before registering your exemption.<br><br>You can save your progress and return later via this portal.<br><br>The exemption details will be logged onto the register as soon as you submit it.<br><br>Enforcing authorities will have access to the register to allow them to check the details you have provided.<br><br>As this is a self-certification, you do not need to do anything else.<br>The Enforcing Authority will only contact you if they have a query about the exemption you have registered.<br><br>We will send you a notification 28 days before your exemption expires.<br></p>"
              },
